      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOW AWESOME (1) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at Warrnambool over 390m behind Paw Natullo (22.93) in a Restricted WIN. Was a winner prior to that. Key runner on his best form. GLIMMER OF HOPE (8) is a consistent type who is having her first try here. Strong winner last time by 1.2 lengths at Warrnambool in Bottom Up - Restricted Win in one of the quickest times on the program (22.33). The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Expected to feature again. PAW QUINTESSA (2) turned in a better effort at Warragul last start, finishing third behind Here Comes Billy (22.92) in a Mix 6/7. Chased the leaders and with a clean run can be prominent. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Leading chance. PAW WHISPER (5) can fill a top-three spot.",
